Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Video games craze
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wq0t
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 6 Dec 1981
Japanese firm Atari sweeps US with new game craze - and a whole new industry. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less